<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <title>Student Helper</title>

    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        .main {
            min-height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .main h1 {
            font-size: 42px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .main h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .main p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .second {
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            margin: 30px auto;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        mark {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .third {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 50px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .third div {
            width: 400px;
            height: 300px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .third div:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-10px);
        }

        .third img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <h1>Student Helper</h1>
        <li>
            <ul><a href="/home">Home</a></ul>
            <ul><a href="/schedule">Schedule</a></ul>
            <ul><a href="/expenses">Expenses</a></ul>
            <ul><a href="/find">Find</a></ul>
            <ul><a href="#">About</a></ul>
            <div class="profile" onclick="window.location.href = '/profile'">
                <img src="<%=user.profile %>" alt="">
            </div>
        </li>
    </nav>

    <div class="main">
        <h1>Hello <%= user.name %></h1>
        <h3>Welcome to Student Helper</h3>
        <p>We help hardworking students like you manage time better.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="second">
        <p>This website helps working students plan their study time, work schedule, and rest.<br>
           A <mark>Student Helper</mark> assists students in balancing their academic and job life.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="third">
        <div><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1584697964192-4e85df3c2e5c" alt="Study Time"></div>
        <div><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554774853-719586f82d77" alt="Working Student"></div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        All rights reserved by Student Helper
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
